subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick moved her No. 10 Chevrolet to the back of the pack in the first of the two Budweiser Duel 150’s, avoided a major crash and finished 17th.
